  "title": "Salad Shop Service Crew",
  "description": "<p>Looking for a service crew in Halal Salad Shop at Raffles Place Area</p><p>5 working days, 6 hours per day (9am - 4pm)  </p><p></p><p>-Responsible for presenting menus to customers.</p><p>-Provide service in a warm and friendly manner to customers such as taking orders, answers questions on meal items and makes recommendations</p><p>-Prepare and complete orders in time manner and present to customers</p><p>-Maintain the cleanliness of the restaurant at all times such as cleaning the table, refill all the necessaries</p><p>-Any other duties assigned</p><p><br /></p><p>-<strong> </strong>1 year of experience in F&B industry</p><p>- Able to work in a team, positive attitude</p><p>- Willing to learn. Good integrity and personality</p><p>- Able to comply with Food Hygiene & Halal Regulations</p><p>- Looking to join a young and energetic team!</p>",
